on, but are most diverse in tropical and subtropical areas (<A href='http://rameau.snv.jussieu.fr/cgi-bin/psyllesexplorer.pl?db=psylles&lang=fr&card=publication&id=3' target='_blank'>Burckhardt, 1987</A>; <A href='http://rameau.snv.jussieu.fr/cgi-bin/psyllesexplorer.pl?db=psylles&lang=fr&card=publication&id=304' target='_blank'>Hollis, 2004</A>).\r\n<p>\r\n(Extract from: <A href='http://rameau.snv.jussieu.fr/cgi-bin/psyllesexplorer.pl?db=psylles&lang=fr&card=publication&id=826' target='_blank'>Ouvrard et al., 2010</A>).
