presenttxt	FLOW (Fulgoromorpha Lists On the WEB) est une base de données sur les Hémiptères Fulgoromorphes accessible sur le web. elle a pour but de permettre aux entomologistes ou tout autre personne intéressée, l'accès à une synthèse de l'ensemble des connaissances biologiques publiées sur ce groupe, d'importance économique majeure.\r\nA terme, ce projet proposera pour plus de 14 000 espèces déjà décrites, des informations taxinomiques, nomenclaturales, morphologiques, étho-écologiques, biogéographiques ou bibliographiques.\r\nFLOW participe au BEFRI (<A href='http://bach.snv.jussieu.fr/befri/'>Biodiversity and Evolution of Fulgoromorpha: a Research Initiative</A>).	FLOW is an on-line database that aims to provide an easy-access synthesys of available biological published primary data on planthoppers (Hemiptera, Fulgoromorpha), a group of major economic importance. It includes information on taxonomy, nomenclature, type depository, bibliography, distribution and various associated biological information as host-plants, parasites of planthoppers of the world including fossiles. Ultimately it will include also photos of types and biotopes, sound recording and molecular data for more than 14000 species currently described. FLOW is a contribution to BEFRI (<A href='http://bach.snv.jussieu.fr/befri/'>Biodiversity and Evolution of Fulgoromorpha: a Research Initiative</A>).	El proyecto FLOW (Fulgoromorpha Lists On the WEB) pone a disposición sobre este sitio WEB, una base de datos sobre Hemiptera Fulgoromorpha. Tiene como objetivo permitir a los entomólogos, o a toda otra persona interesada, disponer de una síntesis fácilmente accesible del conjunto de conocimientos biológicos publicados sobre este grupo. A este término, para mas de 14000 especies ya descritas, el proyecto proporcionará las informaciones tanto taxonómicas como morfológicas, eto-ecológicas, biogeográficas o bibliográficas.\r\nFLOW participa al proyecto BEFRI (<A href='http://bach.snv.jussieu.fr/befri/'>Biodiversity and Evolution of Fulgoromorpha: a Research Initiative</A>).	O FLOW é uma base de dados on-line cujo objetivo é promover uma síntese de fácil acesso dos dados primários já publicados sobre Fulgoromorpha, um grupo de grande importância econômica. \r\nO FLOW inclui dados sobre taxonomia, nomenclatura, depósito de tipos, bibliografia, distribuição e várias informações biológicas associadas, como plantas-hospedeiras, parasitas de Fulgoromorpha mundiais e até fósseis. Por fim, o FLOW incluirá fotos de tipos e biótopos, gravações sonoras e dados moleculares para mais de 14000 espécies já descritas. O FLOW é uma contribuição ao BEFRI (<A href='http://bach.snv.jussieu.fr/befri/'>Biodiversity and Evolution of Fulgoromorpha: a Research Initiative</A>).\r\n\r\n\r\n	FLOW is an on-line database that aims to provide an easy-access synthesys of available biological published primary data on planthoppers (Hemiptera, Fulgoromorpha), a group of major economic importance. It includes information on taxonomy, nomenclature, type depository, bibliography, distribution and various associated biological information as host-plants, parasites of planthoppers of the world including fossiles. Ultimately it will include also photos of types and biotopes, sound recording and molecular data for more than 14000 species currently described. FLOW is a contribution to BEFRI (<A href='http://bach.snv.jussieu.fr/befri/'>Biodiversity and Evolution of Fulgoromorpha: a Research Initiative</A>).	anta	2007-01-16	guest	2018-01-05	FLOW is an on-line database that aims to provide an easy-access synthesys of available biological published primary data on planthoppers (Hemiptera, Fulgoromorpha), a group of major economic importance. It includes information on taxonomy, nomenclature, type depository, bibliography, distribution and various associated biological information as host-plants, parasites of planthoppers of the world including fossiles. Ultimately it will include also photos of types and biotop